<descript>
<abstract>This dataset is intended for read-only use. The purpose of these data is to provide display, identification, and analysis tools for determining current boundary information for Forest Service managers, GIS specialists, and others.</abstract>
<purpose>This dataset represents boundaries of areas that close federal lands to settlement, sale, location, or entry under some or all the general land and mineral laws to maintain other public values or purposes. A withdrawal area has one or more associated segregations. A segregation is a specific activity which the area has been withdrawn from, such as settlement, sale, location, or entry.</purpose>
</descript>
